# Ignore entire desktop app directory
**/trio-sync-desk-main/**
**/dist-electron-build/**
**/release-builds/**
**/_dist-electron-build-temp/**
**/_release-builds-temp/**

# Ignore build artifacts
**/*.exe
**/*.aab
**/*.apk
**/*.msi
**/*.dmg

# Large files
**/*.zip
**/*.tar
**/*.gz
**/*.rar

# Node modules from other projects
**/node_modules/

# System files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
